TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Estimation of Mixed Regression, Autoregression, Moving Average, and Distributed Lag Models
AU  - Hannan, E. J.
AU  - Nicholls, D. F.
AB  - [In this paper a procedure is presented for the (asymptotically) efficient estimation of the parameters of autoregressive moving average models with exogenous variables. The estimation of distributed lag models is discussed as a particular case of models of this form. Finally a number of numerical examples are described.]
