TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Remark on the Core of an Atomless Economy
AU  - Schmeidler, David
AB  - [In an atomless economy any allocation that is not blocked by "small" coalitions is in the core. Hence, in such an economy, a competitive equilibrium is characterized by the blocking power of part of the coalitions which excludes all "big" coalitions.]
